  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Heat the onions, ginger, and garlic until the onions are translucent.",
    "Add the mustard seeds and cumin seeds and let them sizzle.",
    "Add the coriander powder, turmeric powder, and red chili powder and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the kombu cold extract and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the coconut milk and stir well.",
    "Add the nutmeg and stir well.",
    "Simmer the curry for 5 minutes or until it thickens.",
    "Season the curry with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the curry hot with steamed rice."
